          <h2 style="font-size:24px;line-height:1.2;font-weight:500;">
        Afghans exit Iran</h2>
        </mj-text>
        <mj-text padding="10px 12px" font-family="Roboto+Serif" color="#000000">
         <p style="font-size:18px;line-height:1.5;">
         <strong>
    Summary: Almost 450,000 undocumented Afghans in Iran have returned to their homeland amid the humanitarian crisis in Afghanistan.</strong>
         </p>
          <p style="font-size:16px;line-height:1.5;">
      In late May, Iran ordered all undocumented migrants, mostly Afghans, to exit the country by July 6, which was estimated to impact 4 out of the 6Mn Afghans living in Iran. As the deadline approached, in just 5 days, almost <a style="text-decoration: none; border-bottom: 2px solid  #102341; color: black;" href="https://link.geopoliticalsummary.com/gs-8-jul-25-spotlight-h2-4-450-000-afghans-crossed-the-border" target="_blank">450,000 Afghans crossed the border</a>, bringing the total this year to over 900,000. 
          </p>
          <p style="font-size:16px;line-height:1.5;">
      These targeted crackdowns are a result of <a style="text-decoration: none; border-bottom: 2px solid  #102341; color: black;" href="https://link.geopoliticalsummary.com/gs-8-jul-25-spotlight-h2-5-growing-economic-pressure" target="_blank">growing economic pressure</a> and security concerns in Iran. Years of international sanctions, inflation, and unemployment have created strong resentment toward migrants. Iran is also concerned that these undocumented migrants could <a style="text-decoration: none; border-bottom: 2px solid  #102341; color: black;" href="https://link.geopoliticalsummary.com/gs-8-jul-25-spotlight-h2-6-become-spies" target="_blank">become spies</a> and lead to potential criminal activities and unrest.
       </p>
        <p style="font-size:16px;line-height:1.5;">
     Afghanistan is facing one of the world's worst humanitarian crises after decades of war. As of 2024, 23.7Mn people needed immediate <a style="text-decoration: none; border-bottom: 2px solid  #102341; color: black;" href="https://link.geopoliticalsummary.com/gs-8-jul-25-spotlight-h2-7-humanitarian-assistance" target="_blank">humanitarian assistance</a> as the nation battles poverty. The takeover of the region by the Taliban in 2021 has reversed progress and worsened conditions.</p>
        </mj-text>
      </mj-column>
    </mj-section>

